{"type":null,"faqId":32873,"title":"【EMUI3.1及以上】拍照-一镜知天下","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:#333333;}\n.s2{color:#444444;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">上能识码，下晓外文；满腹经纶，博大精深——不用怀疑，这些就是在说</span><a href=\"http://cn.club.vmall.com/forum.php?gid=327%22 \\t %22_blank\"><span class=\"s2\">EMUI</span></a><span class=\"s1\">3.1的相机app。想要知道这是为什么吗？那就快详戳大图，看看让相机app带你“一镜知天下”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">作为EMUI3.1中一个学识渊博的相机app，不仅要会拍摄，还能扫码辨外语，神马外文路牌、外文菜单、条码，只需用镜头一扫，瞬间变成你懂的信息，所见即所得。外出、旅行、血拼利器，尽在你手中！遇到这样的相机app，你就从了把！</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>进入相机并将二维码放到取景界面，屏幕会自动进行识别，发现二维码后会给出用户提示，用户点击后即可查看识别内容。支持多种二维码类型：微信、email、网址、文本、WIFI、短信，还支持条形码，并能查找商品信息哦~</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>比百度翻译识别速度更快、识别结果更准确的神翻译：用户点击进入相机，切换到在线翻译模式，之后对着报纸，登机牌，警告信息，路牌等文字信息，会进行文字识别并联网翻译，翻译回来的内容显示在界面上。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>有“一镜知天下”的神机在手，就不怕出门在外没翻译了~世界各地随你畅游！</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7593","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748434000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":38,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"拍照,镜知天下","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}